    <title>域名绑定</title>
    <url>/2025/01/14/%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="前期准备"><a href="#前期准备" class="headerlink" title="前期准备"></a>前期准备</h1><blockquote>
<ol>
<li>已经在cloudflare上托管的域名</li>
<li>1panel面板</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h1><div class="tabs" id="tab-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#1-1">在1panel面板的步骤</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#1-2">在cloudflare的步骤</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="1-1"><ol>
<li>找到应用商店的<code>OpenResty</code><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114004259637.png?sign=DoS-JMlqzmELPfOTCD8eFW-6KK0CQFhzQtDfz4J-p3s=:0" alt="image-20250114004259568"></li>
<li>执行安装</li>
<li>进入<code>网站</code>这个界面并点击<code>创建网站</code></li>
<li>点击<code>反向代理</code>,按照要求填写即可<br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114004751774.png?sign=Zrbt-1fUtfhafNPtUmU7rJCZDSTkO8KccNwuc-6USzk=:0" alt="image-20250114004751713"></li>
<li>点击<code>证书</code>，点击<code>上传证书</code>，按照在cloudflare申请的证书上传即可<br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114004916286.png?sign=EZVoj6IXO09x7_WCzkRHiHoSce6RHB2ma5G6E1NTZqk=:0" alt="image-20250114004916189"><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114005821111.png?sign=EzCVImC-n0090gjytiTVF7E0mGDAKuBMvdr8q4lRckc=:0" alt="image-20250114005821039"></li>
<li>回到<code>网站</code>这个页面，点击<code>配置</code></li>
<li>点击<code>HTTPS</code>，点击<code>启用HTTPS</code>，点击<code>保存</code><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114010152860.png?sign=din9fai0a6Gr10bQt-MKi13TsuZzoKTmRFNUJbej2nc=:0" alt="image-20250114010152759"><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114010238479.png?sign=aSsjYF_FGr5kRxU2Od-hnorukj2NlfWYr0UonaOmLN8=:0" alt="image-20250114010238363"></li>
</ol></div><div class="tab-pane" id="1-2"><ol>
<li>访问你的<a class="link" href="https://dash.cloudflare.com/">cloudflare<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>的界面</li>
<li>看到你转入的域名了嘛，点进去<br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114004509005.png?sign=15oFcE3kMA6nSX7ZdaAGlfrzSREXlkyOovO-quDIfxw=:0" alt="image-20250114004508870"></li>
<li>找到左侧的<code>DNS</code>，添加DNS记录即可</li>
<li>点击<code>SSL/TLS</code></li>
<li>点击<code>源服务器</code></li>
<li>点击<code>创建证书</code><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114005217446.png?sign=1ubVQCZD1vZ03BqE2KdIPVF43nT6b2so04LrhS3vkoA=:0" alt="image-20250114005217382"></li>
<li>选择你的<code>证书有效期</code>，一般是15年，点击<code>创建</code><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114005240258.png?sign=nl3BEiWqy2EIBEaX_A60BwDYo4mqqekZ3UYN0kFSrt0=:0" alt="image-20250114005240165"></li>
<li>选择密钥格式为<code>PEM</code><br><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="http://107.175.213.203:3939/d/%E4%B8%89%E5%BF%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/20250114005430848.png?sign=bQHzPfQ33x8kgwJKuORmge1Oi1MBT-m_j-sBHv92njs=:0" alt="image-20250114005430780"></li>
<li>创建一个记事本记住<code>源证书</code>(也就是公钥)和<code>私钥</code></li>
</ol></div></div></div>

<p>接着就可以通过配置的域名进行访问了</p>
]]></content>
